Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, we're going to raise \NKaleido Star's curtain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star, you \Nshould keep your room brightly lit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, have you ever thought \N"I can't do this anymore"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though you work to your limit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there is nothing you can do about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there is somebody waiting for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone who encourages \Nyou and is tough on you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Friends should be able to trust each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I'm not the only \None having a hard time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not! I'm not!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is looking \Nfor must be someplace{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has to be somewhere {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:01:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your dream comes true \Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember how I used to say \NI could make it to the end?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must have been pretending to be tough{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything I did was reckless \Nand it never got me anywhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you alone were always beside me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is looking \Nfor must be somewhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can start going forward {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From this moment, something will start{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe that {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The light I haven't seen yet is \Nbeaming toward the promised place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your dream comes true \Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go to the river and do the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte, Julie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't agree with that Yuri guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's more like we were fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shush!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's way past "working hard."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks super miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me, it's pretty extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, I'd like, die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how she can endure that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bit of renewed respect for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of training is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:19.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Amazing Intensive Training Continues."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the day they perform \Nthe legendary great maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're holding special events every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want everyone to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The atmosphere at Kaleido \NStage is really heating up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's all this about \Nmaking the tickets non-refundable
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if they can't perfect \Nthe legendary maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I personally feel pain when I think of \Nhow they suddenly cancelled "Freedom"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though it was the \Nprevious owner's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Refunding the money at that time \Nwas very tough financially.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we made everything clear this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sold the tickets only to those \Nwho understood the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then have you gotten any complaints?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to rumor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the last person to attempt \Nthis great maneuver
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he died in an accident during practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the maneuver is that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I definitely want the \Nperformance to succeed this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This channel will be broadcasting \Nlive on the day of the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how is the progress of the \Nlegendary great maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I doubt they will perfect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 99% certain that the \Nperformance will be cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the publicity about \Nthe legendary great maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the attendance is picking up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, sales of related \Nmerchandise are going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All thanks to this legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the cancellation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll announce that Layla and I \Nwill attempt the maneuver again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing so, we can generate \Neven more publicity and--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we cancel the performance, \Nwe can end Kaleido Stage too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to sell Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep letting you manage it, I'm \Nafraid that we'll lose a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet old man Kenneth knew this was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he backed out of \Nthe investment so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Mia, Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Jonathan and everyone doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to chitchat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This? Special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special training?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrible, doing \Nsomething like this to Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you work hard, you can't \Ncatch up with Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:06:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being reckless is my specialty. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, please let Sora rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take her to the lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's training,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she did that until \Nshe became so bruised and tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Ken, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he would protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to practice! Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:26.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't catch up with Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You have to get more rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to catch up with Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't rest, you'll break down, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, but I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause Miss Layla has already \Nadvanced to more difficult training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla is practicing too, \Nbruising herself all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That legendary great maneuver...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a much harder \Nmaneuver than we ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do about that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's better that we don't tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means nothing if you did it by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want you to try hard until you \Ncan do it ten times consecutively.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm beginning to understand what \Nthe legendary great maneuver is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I could do that kind of maneuver, \Nit would be truly wonderful, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't do that with my \Npartner in her current state.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't you going to eat any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I have lost my appetite today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my meals in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it ten times consecutively.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will advance to the next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to receive the applause \Nthat makes my whole body tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, no matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to perfect the legendary \Ngreat maneuver with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just keeping the posture \Nitself is hard enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But to swing that high on top of it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how long are you going to rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Miss Layla \Nseems irritated somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even said she wanted to \Nhave meals all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte's cooking is kinda bad, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying! You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. Your cooking is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla is irritated \Nbecause I'm not good enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I'm really able to be \NMiss Layla's partner like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After a week, she finally \Nstarted showing stability,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it looks like she's lost her motivation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go help Charlotte and Julie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why won't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like, "Try harder,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"be strong,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or "you can never be my \Npartner if you're like that."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Kenneth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What business brought him? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, coming all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that woeful face, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you have no \Nfighting spirit at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hardly look capable of doing \Nthat legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's tired now because she \Njust finished training.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess everything is just \Nthe way those guys wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those squirts who are \Ninvesting in Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of them think you will perfect \Nthe legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the maneuver is not perfected,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they think it will be all right \Nas long as they can make a profit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through the events leading up \Nto the day of the actual event.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, they're thinking it'll be better \Nif the performance is cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, they can save on the expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about the audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you say with confidence that you \Nwill never disappoint the audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you say with confidence that you \Nwill perfect that maneuver with Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you say with confidence \Nthat you're Layla's partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like, "Try harder,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"be strong,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or "you can never be my \Npartner if you're like that."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you ask her something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's desperately trying to rouse \Nherself even though she's discouraged!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think I'll go \Ninside and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me some coffee, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ken Robbins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell him that I \Nwould perfect it by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla called me her partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I just let it go to my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having come this far, I finally realize that \Nmy abilities are completely inadequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel like running away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing more than enough, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if it's too tough, I \Nthink it's okay to back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Miss Layla will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla told me once...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nuisance if you're going to prepare \Nyourself with a half-baked attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If quitting is better for Miss Layla, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very kind of you to \Ncome all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew Sora was very a talented \Ngirl and I expected a lot from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never realized she was so good she \Ncould attempt that legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is this the first time since Arlon Brass?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that accident still weigh on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My feeling of regret has not disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was reliable and very responsible,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that challenge was reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who died attempting the legendary \Ngreat maneuver at Kaleido Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was Arlon Brass, the top star at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I confirmed the story with Jean, \Nso there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those investors at Kaleido Stage \Nmust have heard the story from Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's understandable why they don't \Nbelieve in the success of maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:16:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you to perfect the \Nmaneuver without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody, including Mr. Yuri, thinks I'm \Nable to perfect the legendary maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the problem is how \NSora will react after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether she can rise out of the depths, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can't do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is absolutely no way that she could \Nperform the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you guys are the ones who created \N"Freedom" when you were at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you back out of the investment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can let us experience how \Nwe can rise up from the bottom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't feel like doing \Nbusiness with those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will deliver this to Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora said she doesn't want dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was told by Miss Layla \Nnot to talk about this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla is not here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's out running.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She's trying to lose weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably, the greater the weight \Ndifference of the two performers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the lower the chance of success \Nof the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Miss Layla realized what \Nthe legendary great maneuver is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's almost time \Nfor her to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Miss Layla has been eating \Nher meals in her room these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard she's not \Nreally eating most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though it seems she was \Ntold not to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla is doing all \Nof this because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's wrong to blame yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partners are supposed to be equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to be a good \Npartner for Miss Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's also trying to be your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've admired her for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. You have \Nsomething I don't possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real fight between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a child, I saw \NKaleido Stage with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so wonderful. Like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will not be my last \Nshow, unless I wish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I have a partner \Nwho can make it possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you guys are the best partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the special training \Nis hard and painful,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made excuses and told myself that I \Ndon't have the skills to be your partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to run away by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never doubt myself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work much harder and catch up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to perfect the legendary \Ngreat maneuver by any means!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came all this way to do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat a lot and build up muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't lose any more weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really rose up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was worth coming all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person who rises up from \Nthe bottom is tougher for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You mean you did this on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wide awake now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me some bourbon, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ken Robbins!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As partners, let's not keep \Nany secrets from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give you qualification \Nto attempt that maneuver yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems like fate is trying to put \Nyou through a more rigorous ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're able to overcome \Nit, the time will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it is a brutal ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reversed Empress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just hit your shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just lost my balance and \Nscratched it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I think you should go \Nto see a doctor for just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She seems to be doing okay. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since I lost weight, I \Npassed out for a moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems my shoulder can somehow hold on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:36.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please... a little longer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please last a little longer. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, it's the day before the actual show.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Miss Layla's injuries were worse than \Nanybody expected, and it was hopeless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In spite of that, just what... \NJust what drives you to go so far?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's the real reason \Nbehind the heroic decision?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star, "An Amazing Bond."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream and \Non towards the sky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.89,0:23:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm here between the sky and the \Nroads, and facing against the wind{\i0}
